Job   Description
1 . Responsible   for   the   development   and   maintenance   of   test   hardware   and
software   for   the   production   testing   of   integrated   circuits .
2 . Develop   PC   based   test   hardware   and   software   for   testing   mixed   signal   IC ’ s .
3 . Develop   mixed   signal   ATE   applications   for   IC   production   testing .
4 . Assist   Product   Engineers   and   IC   Design   Engineers   in   product   evaluation   and
qualification .

